snippet.title: Origami Lovers Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Hi everyone, it is time for big news.

You can now officially wishlist Origami Lovers on Steam! Using the link below, you can make sure the release isn’t going to slip past you. Give it a watch using the link below.

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2513170/Origami_Lovers/

We hope you are as excited as we are and welcome you to take the final steps towards the release together with us.🌸
